review: I would like to express my sincere gratitude to Dr. Swarna and especially her staff, at their Hyderabad Centre for all the help extended during our consultation and treatment for one of our family members! I was very impressed to witness the hygienic/covid protocols that were strictly followed at each stage! Thankful for a very sound professional and at the same time, a very friendly advice provided while making us feel very comfortable throughout! Strongly recommended this centre for anyone who is seeking consultation related to IVF!
